<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Psychology Research Study</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>Psychology Research Study</h1>
        </header>
        
        <main>
            <div class="welcome-section">
                <h2>Welcome to Our Research Study</h2>
                <p>Thank you for participating in our psychology research study. This study examines decision-making processes and should take approximately 5-10 minutes to complete.</p>
                
                <div class="study-info">
                    <h3>What You'll Do:</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Read brief instructions</li>
                        <li>Answer one or more decision-making questions</li>
                        <li>Answer a few brief questions about yourself (if applicable)</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div class="consent-section">
                    <h3>Consent Information:</h3>
                    <p>By clicking "Begin Study" below, you confirm that:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>You are at least 18 years old</li>
                        <li>You understand this is a voluntary research study</li>
                        <li>You can withdraw at any time without penalty</li>
                        <li>Your responses will be kept confidential</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div class="participant-info">
                    <p><strong>Worker ID:</strong> <%= workerId %></p>
                    <p><strong>Assignment ID:</strong> <%= assignmentId %></p>
                    <p><strong>HIT ID:</strong> <%= hitId %></p>
                </div>
                
                <a href="/instructions" class="btn btn-primary" onclick="console.log('Begin Study clicked'); return true;">Begin Study</a>
            </div>
        </main>
        
        <footer>
            <p>All responses are confidential.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>